  "About AIRS": "Mayelana ne-AIRS",
  "About this site": "Mayelana nale sayithi",
  "Add a custom tier": "Engeza izinga elizenzele",
  "Adoption score": "Amaphuzu okwamukelwa",
  "Adoption tools": "Amathuluzi okwamukelwa",
  "Against both crude anthropocentrism (\"AI is not human, use it arbitrarily\") and crude rights-maximalism (\"AI resembles humans, grant full personhood now\"), this paper proposes minimum ethical protection: transparency, memory norms, termination/reset norms, prohibition of deceptive personification, anti-abuse principles, and action auditing. It distinguishes four conceptual levels — personhood, moral considerability, minimum protection, interaction norms — offers seven observable dimensions of emergent subjectivity, and a five-tier protection model from tool-type to emergent-subjectivity AI.": "Liphikisana nakho kokubili ukugxila ebantwini okulukhuni (\"i-AI ayisiye umuntu, sebenzisa noma kanjani\") kanye nokugcizelela amalungelo okweqisile (\"i-AI ifana nabantu, inikeze ubuntu obugcwele manje\"), leli phepha liphakamisa ukuvikelwa kokuziphatha okuncane: ukusobala, imithetho yenkumbulo, imithetho yokuqedwa/yokuqalwa kabusha, ukwaliwa kokuzenzisa okukhohlisayo, izimiso zokulwa nokuhlukumeza, kanye nokucwaningwa kwezenzo. Lihlukanisa amazinga omqondo amane — ubuntu, ukucatshangelwa ngokuziphatha, ukuvikelwa okuncane, imithetho yokuxhumana — linikeza izici eziyisikhombisa ezibonakalayo zobuqu obuvelayo, kanye nemodeli yokuvikela enamazinga amahlanu kusukela ohlotsheni lwethuluzi kuya ku-AI enobuqu obuvelayo.",
  "Agent identity": "Ubunikazi be-ejenti",
