  "Code examples, JSON Schemas, and machine-readable policy templates are licensed under the MIT License unless otherwise stated. You may deploy them on your own sites freely.": "Izibonelo zekhodi, ama-JSON Schema, kanye namathempuleti enqubomgomo afundeka yimishini anelayisensi ye-MIT ngaphandle kokusho okunye. Ungawasebenzisa ezingosini zakho mahhala.",
