  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Layalwa ngemuva Kwengqungquthela Yezokuphepha Kwe-AI yaseBletchley futhi iholwa nguYoshua Bengio kanye nochwepheshe abangaphezu kwe-100 abavela emazweni acishe abe ngu-30 kanye ne-UN, i-OECD ne-EU, lo mbiko ozimele uhlanganisa ubufakazi bemvelaphi bamanje ngamakhono nezingozi ze-AI esesikhondlweni — uphawula ukuthi amanye amasistimu manje angabona uma ehlolwa futhi alungise ukuziphatha kwawo ngokufanele.",
