  "Convert rights declarations into a workable licensing market instead of a binary open/closed web.": "Guqula izimemezelo zamalungelo zibe imakethe yelayisensi esebenzayo esikhundleni sewebhu evulekile/evaliwe eyimbili.",
  "Copied ✓": "Kukopishiwe ✓",
