  "Correct positioning: independent research drafts, protocol proposals, and an open specification experiment.": "Ukubekwa okulungile: amadrafu ocwaningo azimele, iziphakamiso zamaphrothokholi, kanye nokuhlolwa kwemininingwane evulekile.",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Belgium (BE) now maps to Dutch instead of French — Flemish speakers are the country’s majority (~60%) over Walloon French speakers (~40%).": "Kulungiswe okuzenzakalelayo kwangaphambilini: iBelgium (BE) manje isihlelwa kusiDashi esikhundleni sesiFulentshi — abakhulumi besiFlemish bayisiningi sezwe (~60%) uma kuqhathaniswa nabakhulumi besiFulentshi baseWalloon (~40%).",
  "Corrected an earlier default: Kazakhstan (KZ) now maps to Kazakh instead of Russian, now that a Kazakh translation exists — the same kind of fix as the earlier Belgium correction.": "Kulungiswe okuzenzakalelayo kwangaphambilini: iKazakhstan (KZ) manje isihlelwa kusiKazakh esikhundleni sesiRashiya, manje njengoba sekukhona ukuhunyushwa kwesiKazakh — uhlobo olufanayo lokulungiswa njengokulungiswa kwangaphambilini kweBelgium.",
  "Could AI Be Conscious?": "Could AI Be Conscious?",
