  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Isibonelo semfundo: i-HMAC-SHA256 enemfihlo eyabelwana ngayo, ebonisa amathokheni elayisensi abophezelwe esicelweni, aphelelwa yisikhathi, futhi angaqinisekiswa. Amathokheni okusebenza kufanele asayinwe ngokungalingani, ngenkinobho yomphakathi yomshicileli etholakala ngaphansi kwe-/.well-known/.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Okunye okuyisishiyagalombili ezingenweni ze-/topics, kulokhu okucwaningwe yi-ejenti ye-AI kunokuhlelwa ngesandla — umthetho ofanayo njengangaphambili: umthombo ngamunye ulandiwe futhi waqinisekiswa uphila, izifinyezo ziyindlela yethu yokuchaza ngamanye amagama, ngaphambi kokuthi kwengezwe noma yini. Izingeno eziyi-14 sekukonke.",
  "Email": "I-imeyili",
  "Emotion Concepts and Their Function in a Large Language Model": "Emotion Concepts and Their Function in a Large Language Model",
  "Empirical Research": "Ucwaningo Lokuhlolwa",
  "English edition →": "Uhlelo lwesiNgisi →",
  "Ensure openness is machine-executable — so goodwill is not discarded as legal uncertainty.": "Qinisekisa ukuthi ukuvuleka kungasetshenziswa yimishini — ukuze umoya omuhle ungalahlwa njengokungaqiniseki ngokomthetho.",
