  "Turns declared rights into executable licensing: quote, pay, verify, audit, revoke.": "Kuguqula amalungelo amenyezelwe abe ukunikezwa kwelayisensi okungasetshenziswa: cela intengo, khokha, qinisekisa, cwaninga, hoxisa.",
  "Twenty languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi, Indonesian, Vietnamese, Greek, Italian, Dutch.": "Izilimi ezingamashumi amabili ziyasebenza sekukonke: isiNgisi, isiShayina Esidabuko, isiShayina Esilula, isiJapane, isiKorea, isiFulentshi, isiJalimane, isiSpanishi, isiPutukezi, isiRashiya, isi-Arabhu, isiTurkey, isiPheresiya, isiBengali, isiHindi, isi-Indonesia, isiVietnam, isiGreek, isi-Italy, nesiDashi.",
  "Two license tiers: a free public tier and a contact-based commercial tier.": "Amazinga elayisensi amabili: izinga lomphakathi elimahhala kanye nezinga lezohwebo elisekelwe ekuxhumaneni.",
  "UI": "Isikhombimsebenzisi",
  "Undefined openness reads as legal uncertainty to AI pipelines and gets cleaned out; only protocolized, machine-readable permission makes content genuinely learnable.": "Ukuvuleka okungachazwanga kufundwa njengokungaqiniseki ngokomthetho ezinqubweni ze-AI futhi kuyasuswa; imvume ephothokholiwe, efundeka yimishini kuphela eyenza okuqukethwe kufundeleke ngempela.",
  "Usage logs and audit trails": "Amarekhodi Okusetshenziswa Kanye Nemikhondo Yokucwaningwa",
