  "Verified dataset markets and collective licensing": "Imakethe Zamasethi Edatha Aqinisekisiwe Kanye Nokunikezwa Kwelayisensi Kwesixuku",
  "Verified in both LTR and RTL contexts: the panel mirrors correctly for Arabic and Persian without any special-casing, using logical CSS positioning.": "Kuqinisekisiwe kuzo zombili izimo ze-LTR ne-RTL: iphaneli iyazibonisa ngokulunge kwesi-Arabhu nesiPheresiya ngaphandle kokuphathwa okukhethekile, isebenzisa ukubekwa kwe-CSS enengqondo.",
  "Verify": "Qinisekisa",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts.": "Umlando wezinguqulo zale sayithi kanye namadrafu ayo amaphrothokholi.",
  "Version history of this site and its protocol drafts. Breaking spec changes are recorded here.": "Umlando wezinguqulo zale sayithi kanye namadrafu ayo amaphrothokholi. Izinguquko ezephulayo zemininingwane zibhalwe lapha.",
  "Versioned specifications, JSON Schemas, and the policy files actually deployed on this site. Every file can be downloaded, validated, and cited directly.": "Imininingwane enezinguqulo, ama-JSON Schema, kanye namafayela enqubomgomo asetshenziswa ngempela kule sayithi. Ifayela ngalinye lingalandwa, liqinisekiswe, futhi licaphunwe ngqo.",
  "Versioning": "Ukwenziwa Kwezinguqulo",
  "Versions": "Izinguqulo",
  "Video and audio companions to the protocols and papers — the AI rights layer, watchable and listenable.": "Amavidiyo nomsindo okuhambisana namaphrothokholi namaphepha — uhlaka lwamalungelo e-AI, olungabukwa nolungalalelwa.",
  "Videos": "Amavidiyo",
  "Want to generate your own policy file?": "Ufuna ukukhiqiza ifayela lenqubomgomo yakho?",
  "Web fonts are loaded from Google Fonts, which receives standard font requests from your browser. No other third-party scripts are used.": "Amafonti ewebhu alayishwa kusuka ku-Google Fonts, etholi izicelo zamafonti ejwayelekile kusiphequluli sakho. Azikho ezinye izikripthi zabanye abasetshenziswa.",
  "What AI systems may do with content: read, summarize, transform, retrieve, train, commercialize, redistribute. The AICR ruleset and the AICL licensing layer make these rights declarable and transactable.": "Lokho amasistimu e-AI angakwenza ngokuqukethwe: ukufunda, ukufingqa, ukuguqula, ukulanda, ukuqeqeshwa, ukukwenza kwezohwebo, ukusatshalaliswa kabusha. Umthetho we-AICR kanye nohlaka lwelayisensi lwe-AICL kwenza lawa malungelo amenyezeleke futhi enziwe imisebenzana ngawo.",
  "What a server can return when an AI crawler requests licensed content without a license token — a machine-actionable quote instead of a dead end.": "Lokho iseva engakubuyisela lapho i-crawler ye-AI icela okuqukethwe okunelayisensi ngaphandle kwethokheni yelayisensi — isicelo sentengo esingasetshenziswa yimishini esikhundleni sesivimbo esingenanjongo.",
  "What this site is": "Ukuthi Le Sayithi Iyini",
  "What this site is not": "Ukuthi Le Sayithi Ayiyona Yini",
  "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration": "When The Machines Deserve Our Consideration",
  "Whether AI may learn, to what depth, for which purposes, and under what obligations. Being read is not being learned from; \"not prohibited\" is not \"learnable\". AIRS and AILP turn learning permission into a graduated, machine-readable spectrum.": "Ukuthi ngabe i-AI ingafunda, ngobunzulu obungakanani, ngezinjongo ezini, futhi ngaphansi kwemithwalo enjani. Ukufundwa akufani nokufundelwa kukho; \"akuvinjelwe\" akufani \"nokufundeleka\". I-AIRS ne-AILP ziguqula imvume yokufunda ibe isipektramu esinyukayo, esifundeka yimishini.",
  "Whitepapers": "Amaphepha Amhlophe",
  "Whitepapers & Docs": "Amaphepha Amhlophe & Imibhalo",
  "Whitepapers remain English-first by design; machine-readable files stay language-neutral.": "Amaphepha amhlophe ahlala eqale ngesiNgisi ngamabomu; amafayela afundeka yimishini ahlala engathathi hlangothi ngokolimi.",
  "Who is behind it": "Ubani Osemuva Kwakho",
  "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections": "Why AI Needs Minimum Ethical Protections",
  "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics": "Why AI might not gain moral standing: Lessons from animal ethics",
  "Why a single allow/deny bit cannot govern AI-era content use — and what a rights layer looks like instead.": "Kungani ibhithi elilodwa lokuvumela/ukwenqaba lingeke lilawule ukusetshenziswa kokuqukethwe kwesikhathi se-AI — kanye nokuthi uhlaka lwamalungelo lubukeka linjani esikhundleni salokho.",
  "Why undefined openness gets cleaned out of training pipelines": "Kungani ukuvuleka okungachazwanga kususwa ezinqubweni zokuqeqeshwa",
  "Wilks, Ladak, and Loughnan (University of Edinburgh) argue that philosophical debate over AI consciousness overlooks psychological research on animal ethics — the same cognitive and social biases that limit moral consideration for animals will likely limit it for AI too, regardless of whether AI ever becomes conscious.": "OWilks, uLadak, noLoughnan (University of Edinburgh) baphikisana ngokuthi impikiswano yefilosofi mayelana nokuqaphela kwe-AI iyeqa ucwaningo lwezengqondo mayelana nokuziphatha ngokuqondene nezilwane — ukukhetha okufanayo kwengqondo nokwenhlalo okulinganisela ukucatshangelwa kokuziphatha kwezilwane kungenzeka kulinganisele nakwe-AI, noma yikuphi ukuthi ngabe i-AI iyoke ibe nokuqaphela.",
  "You are leaving AGIRight.org": "Uyashiya i-AGIRight.org",
