  "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” now published in English as the canonical edition; the Chinese original manuscript remains available and both versions cross-link.": "“AICL: AI Ingestion & Capability Layer” manje ishicilelwe ngesiNgisi njengohlelo olusemthethweni; umbhalo wokuqala wesiShayina uyatholakala futhi zombili izinguqulo ziyaxhumana.",
  "“Protocolized Openness” confirmed as an English-language paper (with Chinese parallel passages) — no separate translation planned.": "“Protocolized Openness” iqinisekisiwe njengephepha lolimi lwesiNgisi (nezigaba ezihambisana zesiShayina) — akukho ukuhunyushwa okuhlukile okuhleliwe.",
